{"tid":228783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(蛇吞象) 海航又掃貨 傳將會成德銀單一大股東","createTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T08:18:54.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df7d4500d86677fbb59bc570bdc5190f4e5ee6dd","tid":228783,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"去年陷入困境的德意志銀行，股權或有變動。有傳聞指出，中國的海航航集團持股已經升至9.9%，成為最大單一股東。<br />\n<br />\n持股提升至9.9%<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，近年大舉到海外投資的海航集團，今次是透過奧地利投資公司C-Quadrat的投資工具入股德銀，股權比例超過卡塔爾皇室及貝萊德。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，海航集團幾日之內就會將文件提交給監管機構，而德銀及C-Quadrat均未有置論。<br />\n<br />\n德銀因為過度發行住房抵押貸款證券（RMBS），而被美國罰款140億美元（1,092億港元），目前正增資80億歐元（約680.6億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n而海航集團股權架構神秘，近日就被傳與中共中紀委書記王歧山的外甥姚慶有關。"},{"pid":"db6733cb21b0121bceeecbca0e7e1a2adae59ff7","tid":228783,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:05:18.000Z","msg":"海航三百零億市值持有成萬億資產<br />\n<br />\n中國夢果然<img src=\"http://g.udn.com.tw/upfiles/B_KA/kalaok/PSN_PHOTO/588/f_9613588_1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fg.udn.com.tw%2Fupfiles%2FB_KA%2Fkalaok%2FPSN_PHOTO%2F588%2Ff_9613588_1.gif&h=6523fe18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce221dcc23a9d620fb81f3780c1852c90d8277e","tid":228783,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"海航真係深不見底"},{"pid":"e46f1f8f3dfeab08265da597fc48af78180462d5","tid":228783,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海航真係深不見底</blockquote><br />\n支共背後撐腰，最重要係識印銀紙"},{"pid":"6dae2d9d66d35e9b0a9783e038375740917e145d","tid":228783,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"海航=雷曼？"},{"pid":"40255d41fc9120eb15fa83646ad0c45f581654b4","tid":228783,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海航=雷曼？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" c